{"type":null,"faqId":47198,"title":"手机屏幕亮度","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">请确认光感应器是否正常。光感应器被异物遮挡可能引起屏幕亮度异常。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">如果感觉屏幕偏亮或偏暗，请调整屏幕亮度。进入“设置”界面，点击“显示”&gt; “亮度”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175537\" style=\"width:5.279861in;height:2.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">超级省电模式下，屏幕会变暗，且只能使用电话、信息和联系人功能。点击“退出”可退出超级省电模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175538\" style=\"width:4.7944446in;height:3.754861in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">如果屏幕曾受到外部冲击，内部液晶可能会破损并导致屏幕亮度或色彩异常。请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以实际手机界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2765","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219095000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":90,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"屏幕亮度","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}